* Zyber looked at the bot standing on a near by hill and listened to the 
music he played, it was beautiful to her ears.
She took a few steps towards him but then stopped, she looked back and saw 
the gazelle running into the distance. She snarled, there went her chance 
for dinner!
Zyber shook her head then turned back to the playing bot, she sniffed the 
air and found no threat to his scent.
She took a few more steps forward then sat down on her haunches, she quietly 
waited for the bot to notice her.*
